      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should reach out but i just dont see the point. everything feels so pointless. it's not even like i'm angry, i'm just... empty. like the world has just stopped moving for me. what's the point of even trying to find a \"next step\" when there's nothing waiting on the other side?",
