      "content": "it just feels like everyone is just reciting a script. \"it makes sense,\" \"you aren't alone,\" \"call this number\"... it's all just noise. it doesn't change the fact that the person who made my life worth living is gone. there's no version of the future where i'm happy again. it feels more like i'm just waiting for the lights to go out anyway.",
